This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves algorithms and data structures, which could place it in the Data Structures (cs.DS) sub-category. The paper also discusses simplification and equivalence of Mapper to other topological constructions, which could place it in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
